## 5. OSPO Compliance Requirements

**MANDATORY Elements:**
1. ✅ Three installation paths (One-Click, Workbench, CLI)
2. ✅ OSPO-compliant disclaimer
3. ✅ License section with reference to LICENSE.md
4. ✅ Bug reporting section with GitHub Issues link
5. ✅ Clear project title and purpose
6. ✅ Technical architecture overview
7. ✅ Post-installation steps

**Tone Requirements:**
- Accessible to both Admins and Developers
- Clear, step-by-step instructions
- No assumptions about CLI knowledge for admin paths
- Professional but friendly tone

---

